   Antelope Valley Air Pollution Control District

   Air Quality Data Summaries: 1994 - 2000

   Lancaster Monitoring Site


   Year Days exceeding state standard Days exceeding 1 hour federal
   standard Days exceeding 8 hour federal standard Max. 1 hr. reading
   parts per million (ppm)
                              1994 62 10 na .14
                              1995 61 5 na .14
                              1996 40 1 na .13
                              1997 13 0 na .12
                              1998 24 8 18 .16
                               1999 1 0 0 .10
                              2000 35 2 28 .14

   State Standard: 0.09 ppm based on 1 hr. average.

   Federal standard: 0.12 ppm based on 1 hr. average.

   0.08 ppm based on 8 hr. average

   Year Days exceeding state standard Days exceeding federal standard Max.
   24 hr. reading
