                                 1996 2 0 67
                                 1997 2 0 54
                                 1998 2 0 80
                                 1999 2 0 85
                                2000 6 0 110

   State Standard: 50 ug/m3 based on 24 hour average.

   Federal Standard: 150 ug/m3 based on 24 hour average.

